### KiriminAja Sandbox API — REST Client Examples
###
### Use with VS Code REST Client or JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Set @apiKey in your environment, or replace with a real key.
###
### Endpoint base: https://tdev.kiriminaja.com
### Auth: Bearer token

@baseUrl = https://tdev.kiriminaja.com
@apiKey = {{KA_API_KEY}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════
# Coverage Area
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### List provinces
POST {{baseUrl}}/coverage-area/province
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{}

### List cities (province_id = 5)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coverage-area/city
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "provinsi_id": 5 }

### Search districts by keyword
POST {{baseUrl}}/coverage-area/district-by-name
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "keyword": "jakarta" }

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════
# Pricing
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Express rate quote
POST {{baseUrl}}/pricing/express
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin_id": 1,
  "destination_id": 2,
  "courier": "all",
  "weight": 1000,
  "item_value": 50000
}

### Instant rate quote
POST {{baseUrl}}/pricing/instant
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service": ["gosend"],
  "item_price": 10000,
  "origin": { "lat": -6.2, "long": 106.8, "address": "Jakarta Pusat" },
  "destination": { "lat": -6.21, "long": 106.81, "address": "Jakarta Selatan" },
  "weight": 1000,
  "vehicle": "motor",
  "timezone": "Asia/Jakarta"
}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════
# Order — Express
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Create express shipment
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/express
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Jl. Example No.1",
  "name": "Test Store",
  "phone": "6281234567890",
  "kecamatan_id": 548,
  "schedule": "2026-01-01 10:00:00",
  "packages": [
    {
      "order_id": "TEST-001",
      "destination_name": "Buyer",
      "destination_phone": "6289876543210",
      "destination_address": "Jl. Destination No.5",
      "destination_kecamatan_id": 3175,
      "weight": 1000,
      "width": 10, "height": 10, "length": 10,
      "item_name": "Test Item",
      "item_value": 100000,
      "shipping_cost": 15000,
      "service": "jne",
      "service_type": "REG23",
      "cod": 0
    }
  ]
}

### Track by order ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/tracking?order_id=TEST-001
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### Cancel shipment
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/void
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "awb": "AWB123456", "reason": "customer cancel" }

###

