### Courier list
POST {{baseUrl}}/others/courier-list
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Courier detail
POST {{baseUrl}}/others/courier-detail
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "courier_code": "jne" }

