# Payment
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### Get payment QR
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "payment_id": "XID-5732095327" }

### KA Credit balance
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment/ka-credit
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}
